[h1]v2.2.0 - Fluid Matrix Menu[/h1]

Adds a Fluid Matrix menu to easily visualize your fluid pool.

[h2]Changelog[/h2]
[list]
  [*]Adds a new fluid matrix menu to show barrel amounts in main water menu
  [*]Fixes an issue where unplumbed fixtures would act/work as plumbed fixture despite not being so
[/list]
